rows.label: tlk000501_08_msg0001
rows.name:
I am carefully checking each
and every one of the letters
Bahn left behind, mo.

rows.label: tlk000501_08_msg0002
rows.name:
Each one was written with
such heart that tears well
up as I read them, mo...

rows.label: tlk000501_08_msg0003
rows.name:
Nilny is ashamed for
suspecting him of slush
funds and pollen orbs, mo.

rows.label: tlk000501_08_msg0004
rows.name:
Bahn is a pure white,
squeaky-clean Nopon, mo!
